OL,3,CMan rebuilding his life after former
OL,4,Cboss spots him in report about
OL,5,Chomelessness
OL,7,FDaren Manders chats to Granada's Emma
OL,8,FSweeney about how his life has changed
OL,9,Fover the last few months.
OL,11,FA man who was sleeping rough is now
OL,12,Frebuilding his life after being
OL,13,Fspotted by his former boss on a
OL,14,FGranada Reports item about
OL,15,Fhomelessness.
OL,17,FDaren Mander had been seeking shelter
OL,18,Fat the Helping Hearts charity in
OL,19,FBlackpool on one of the coldest nights
OL,20,Fof the year back in February.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
