PN,39302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778850694
OL,3,CMan rebuilding his life after former
OL,4,Cboss spots him in report about
OL,5,Chomelessness
OL,7,FHe'd been rough sleeping for three
OL,8,Fmonths following a marriage breakdown.
OL,9,FSpeaking to Granada Reports at the
OL,10,Ftime, he said the 'atrocious weather'
OL,11,Fwas making life even harder.
OL,13,FAfter appearing on the programme,
OL,14,FDaren's former boss Kevin Butler
OL,15,Frecognised him at once, and was struck
OL,16,Fby his plight.
OL,18,FDaren is now learning new skills, has
OL,19,Fa roof over his head, and has
OL,20,Fambitions to start his own business.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778850694
OL,3,CMan rebuilding his life after former
OL,4,Cboss spots him in report about
OL,5,Chomelessness
OL,7,FDaren said: "I've been volunteering
OL,8,Fand learning new skills with my good
OL,9,Ffriend Kevin. I've been doing things
OL,10,Flike slabbing, fencing, plastering."
OL,12,FLife is very different for Daren now,
OL,13,Fcompared to when Granada Reports first
OL,14,Fmet him in February.
OL,16,FHe said: "I was at my wits end.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778850694
OL,3,CMan rebuilding his life after former
OL,4,Cboss spots him in report about
OL,5,Chomelessness
OL,7,F"I was getting help and support from
OL,8,FHelping Hearts, but nothing else. I
OL,9,Fwasn't getting anywhere. But now my
OL,10,Flife has changed completely, and for
OL,11,Fthe better."
OL,13,FDaren was living in a tent at the time
OL,14,Fand spoke to Granada Reports, he says,
OL,15,Fto make "people aware of homelessness".
OL,17,FBut, in a twist of fate, old friend
OL,18,FKevin Butler saw him being interviewed
OL,19,Fand got in touch with him after seeing
OL,20,Fhis story.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778850694
OL,3,CMan rebuilding his life after former
OL,4,Cboss spots him in report about
OL,5,Chomelessness
OL,7,FKevin said: "I was just having my tea
OL,8,Fwatching Granada Reports, and I saw
OL,9,FDaren and I thought, I know who that
OL,10,Fis.
OL,12,F"I know him from years ago and thought
OL,13,F- I've got to help."
OL,15,F"I know he's a great guy, he's got a
OL,16,Fheart of gold."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
