OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778850694
OL,3,CMan rebuilding his life after former
OL,4,Cboss spots him in report about
OL,5,Chomelessness
OL,7,FKevin is now in the process of helping
OL,8,FDaren set up his own gardening
OL,9,Fbusiness, and Daren says he owes Kevin
OL,10,Fa lot: "It's like fate, because if
OL,11,FKevin hadn't been watching the news
OL,12,Fthat night, I wouldn't be here now, I
OL,13,Fwouldn't be in this position.
OL,15,F"I owe Kevin and his family a lot for
OL,16,Feverything they've done for me and
OL,17,Fhelping me get back on my feet. I do
OL,18,Fappreciate it so much."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
